high_descs: Turn to your left and walk across the room to the sink.
Pick up the knife that is in front of the small sink on the left.
Place the knife in the small sink on the left, turn the water on, rinse the knife with water, turn the water off, and remove the knife from the sink.
Step back away from the sink while holding the knife.
Place the knife back on the counter, in front of the small sink on the left.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean knife on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left, head to the sink.
Pick up the knife on the counter in front of the sink.
Wash the knife in the left sink.
Take the the cleaned knife, turn around to face the sink again.
Put the cleaned knife on the counter in front of the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned knife on the counter in front of the sink.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is in the front of the left sink basin.
Rinse the knife off in the left sink basin before picking it back up.
Turn around 360 degrees to face the sink again.
Place the knife down on the counter in front of the left sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean knife on the counter.
